text: The 5th World Freestyle Skating Championships were held in Geisingen, Germany from October 21 to October 23, 2011. 27 countries took part in the competition. ==Medal table== ==References== Category:Roller skating competitions Category:2011 in German sport Category:2010s in Baden-Württemberg Category:2011 in roller sports
